Module com.example.epj2
Package com.example.epj2.model.rent

Class Invoice

java.lang.Object
com.example.epj2.model.rent.Invoice
public class Invoice extends Object
Represents the rental invoice. This class provides methods to access and manipulate invoice attributes.

  • Constructor Details

    • Invoice

      public Invoice(int rentId, String userId, String userLicence, String vehicleId, double primaryPrice, double finalPrice, double promotion, double discount, double distance, LocalDateTime dateTime)
      Constructs a new Invoice object.
      Parameters:
      rentId - the identifier of the rent that invoice is for
      userId - the identification document number of a user (passport number if the user is foreigner, ID card number otherwise)
      userLicence - the driver licence number of the user
      vehicleId - the identifier of the electric vehicle
      primaryPrice - the primary price of the rent
      finalPrice - the final price of the rent
      promotion - the promotion value of the rent
      discount - the discount value of the rent
      distance - the distance coefficient of the rent
      dateTime - the date and time of the rent
